# .pull-ignore — extra patterns to skip when pulling from remote
# Uses rsync exclude syntax (similar to .gitignore).
#
# The following are always excluded (hardcoded):
#   .git/  .ssh/  __pycache__/  *.pyc  .env  agent.toml
#   config.yaml  SOUL.md  node_modules/
#
# Add your own patterns below:

# logs/
# sessions/
# workspace/
